# ═══ Default-DENY gitignore for the public repo ═══
# Everything is ignored unless explicitly allowed. Reports: PDFs only.
# Toolkit: markdown + LICENSE only. A stray file cannot be committed by accident.

# 1) deny everything
*

# 2) allow the repo's own files
!.gitignore
!README.md
!DISCLAIMER.md
!PUBLISH.md

# 3) allow reports/ — PDFs, figures (png+csv), per-report READMEs, .gitkeep
!reports/
!reports/**/
!reports/**/*.pdf
!reports/**/*.png
!reports/**/*.csv
!reports/**/README.md
!reports/**/.gitkeep

# 4) allow toolkit/ — markdown and the licence only
!toolkit/
!toolkit/**/
!toolkit/**/*.md
!toolkit/LICENSE

# 5) re-deny dangerous shapes everywhere (belt and braces)
**/*_internal.*
**/*.py
**/.env*
**/*.key
**/*apikey*
**/*secret*
**/*credentials*
